query:
INSERT INTO realtime.active_period (
                        alert_id,
                        start_time,
                        end_time
                    )
                    SELECT
                        unnest($1::uuid[]),
                        unnest($2::timestamptz[]),
                        unnest($3::timestamptz[])
                    ON CONFLICT (alert_id, start_time) DO UPDATE SET end_time = EXCLUDED.end_time
